parameters.name: graphIdentifier
parameters.description: The unique identifier of the Neptune Analytics graph.

parameters.name: maxResults
parameters.description: The maximum number of results to be fetched by the API.

nested_items.name: queries
nested_items.description: A list of current openCypher queries.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: A string representation of the id of the query.

nested_items.name: queryString
nested_items.description: The actual query text. The queryString may be truncated if the actual query string is too long.

nested_items.name: waited
nested_items.description: The amount of time, in milliseconds, the query has waited in the queue before being picked up by a worker thread.

nested_items.name: elapsed
nested_items.description: The running time of the query, in milliseconds.
